<plot>"Express" is a metaphor, an image, a way of looking at things. But it's also the best, yet unsurpassed, delivery company. No matter the time, the weather or the weight of the package, your parcel will be delivered to its destination with a frightening efficiency! Throughout "Express", strange relationships are revived, coincidences interrupted, and emotional, even explosive, exchanges take place. Inside an elevator on its way to the underground parking, three men meet a mysterious delivery man who holds them hostage.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?185921</url></doc>
